{"tid":2284424,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"去年9月屯門休班警遇襲 警拘25歲男子","createTime":"2020-11-13T09:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T16:25:26.000Z","uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6d641165fd48036e67d9e9711a8f78344a15fd","tid":2284424,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"去年9月14日晚上，大批示威者於屯門市廣場內聚集，其間一名休班警途經時遭示威者襲擊，手機亦被毁壞。至昨日（12日）早上，屯門警區重案組於黃大仙區拘捕一名25歲姓謝本地男子，涉嫌非法集結及刑事毁壞，他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201113/s00001/1605258915846/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%9825%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605258915846%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B49%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%259825%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=a6abb6f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605258915846%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B49%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%259825%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590&h=c121c89d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201113/s00001/1605258915846/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%9825%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90</a>"},{"pid":"68fc37db609bb808bee5c35608bada0bc9ca75ed","tid":2284424,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T